<h2><a href="http://peakoil.com/forums/the-oil-curse-how-petroleum-wealth-shapes-the-development-o-t64758.html?sid=1dbb219594705cc1d9976b0c66b7130f">The Oil Curse: How Petroleum Wealth Shapes the Development o</a></h2>
 <div style="display: none !important;">General discussions of the systemic, societal and civilisational effects of depletion.<br/></div>
<p>
<strong>Moderator:</strong> <a href="http://peakoil.com/forums/pops-u29.html?sid=1dbb219594705cc1d9976b0c66b7130f" style="color: #00AA00;" class="username-coloured">Pops</a>
